      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a dependable choice for daily driving. While the exterior shows some minor signs of age like small paint chips and the interior has light wear on the upholstery, the car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. All major systems, including the brakes and electronics, are in solid working order.",
