    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable ride! It's a solid, honest vehicle that has served its previous owners well and still has plenty of life left to give. While you'll find some typical cosmetic wear and minor mechanical needs consistent with its age, it remains a reliable choice for anyone seeking a functional car at a great value. It\u2019s the perfect opportunity to own a capable vehicle that's ready to work for you!",
