      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled distinction. This vehicle remains in superlative, showroom condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the secondary market. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
